2. Run FSSEEK Bulk Import
3. Get error
Description Updated: FS SEEK Bulk Import Errors:   Violation of Primary KEY constraint PK_SA_FSDLP_Matches Duplicate Key in object dbo.SA_FSDLP_Matches

Next Steps Updated: Dev reviewed the latest applet logs uploaded on the 7th. Then, as far as we're aware, the scan worked, and they could not reproduce the issue or come up with a better path forward at this time. 

We are waiting to see if the scan has the same problem since it takes weeks to complete.
